---
title: "Sequence Diagram: Marcare Prezență Studenți"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Teacher as Profesor
    participant UI as Teacher Dashboard
    participant SessionSvc as Session Service
    participant AttendanceSvc as Attendance Service
    participant HTTP as HTTP Client
    participant SessionAPI as /api/sessions/create.php
    participant AttendanceAPI as /api/attendance/save.php
    participant SessionModel as Session Model
    participant AttendanceModel as Attendance Model
    participant DB as MySQL Database

    Teacher->>UI: Selectează curs
    UI->>SessionSvc: getByCourse(courseId)
    SessionSvc->>HTTP: GET /api/sessions/getByCourse.php
    HTTP->>DB: SELECT study groups pentru curs
    DB-->>HTTP: Lista study_groups
    HTTP-->>UI: Study groups afișate

    Teacher->>UI: Selectează study group
    UI->>SessionSvc: getByStudyGroup(studyGroupId)
    SessionSvc->>HTTP: GET /api/students/getByStudyGroup.php
    HTTP->>DB: SELECT students<br/>FROM study_group_members
    DB-->>HTTP: Lista studenți
    HTTP-->>UI: Studenți afișați în UI

    Teacher->>UI: Selectează laborator (1-14)
    Teacher->>UI: Selectează dată
    Teacher->>UI: Marchează prezența<br/>fiecărui student

    opt Adăugare studenți guest
        Teacher->>UI: Click "Adaugă student"
        UI->>UI: Modal cu căutare studenți
        Teacher->>UI: Caută și adaugă student
        UI->>UI: Adaugă în lista temporară
    end

    Teacher->>UI: Click "Salvează prezența"

    UI->>UI: Validare:<br/>- Toate câmpurile complete?<br/>- Lab nu e deja marcat?

    alt Validare failed
        UI-->>Teacher: Mesaj eroare
    else Validare success
        UI->>SessionSvc: createSession(sessionData)

        SessionSvc->>HTTP: POST /api/sessions/create.php<br/>{course_id, study_group_id,<br/>laboratory_number, session_date}

        HTTP->>SessionAPI: HTTP Request

        SessionAPI->>SessionAPI: Validare date intrare

        SessionAPI->>SessionModel: create(sessionData)

        SessionModel->>DB: START TRANSACTION

        SessionModel->>DB: INSERT INTO sessions<br/>(course_id, study_group_id,<br/>laboratory_number, session_date)

        DB-->>SessionModel: session_id generat

        SessionModel->>DB: SELECT students<br/>FROM study_group_members<br/>WHERE study_group_id = ?

        DB-->>SessionModel: Lista studenți (IDs)

        loop Pentru fiecare student
            SessionModel->>DB: INSERT INTO attendance<br/>(student_id, session_id,<br/>status='absent')
        end

        SessionModel->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

        SessionModel-->>SessionAPI: {success: true, session_id}

        SessionAPI-->>HTTP: Response cu session_id

        HTTP-->>SessionSvc: Session created

        SessionSvc-->>UI: Session ID returnat

        UI->>AttendanceSvc: saveAttendance(sessionId, records)

        AttendanceSvc->>HTTP: POST /api/attendance/save.php<br/>{session_id, records:[<br/>{student_id, status}, ...]}

        HTTP->>AttendanceAPI: HTTP Request

        AttendanceAPI->>AttendanceModel: updateBatch(records)

        AttendanceModel->>DB: START TRANSACTION

        loop Pentru fiecare student marcat present
            AttendanceModel->>DB: UPDATE attendance<br/>SET status = 'present'<br/>WHERE student_id = ? AND session_id = ?
        end

        AttendanceModel->>DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION

        AttendanceModel-->>AttendanceAPI: {success: true}

        AttendanceAPI-->>HTTP: Success response

        HTTP-->>AttendanceSvc: Attendance saved

        AttendanceSvc-->>UI: Success

        UI->>UI: Afișare mesaj succes<br/>"Prezența a fost înregistrată!"

        UI->>UI: Reset formular

        UI->>SessionSvc: Refresh istoric sesiuni

        UI-->>Teacher: Dashboard actualizat
    end

    Note over Teacher,DB: Toată operația este<br/>tranzacțională pentru<br/>consistență date
